These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bongani, havana, chaman
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, domino, poker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, may, august, december
House: ranch-style, palace, townhouse, gothic-revival
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
 2. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
 3. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 5. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the ranch-style house##8
 6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the right of the baccarat-smoker##5
 8. the person playing poker is between the palace house and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 9. the gothic-revival house is the person playing domino##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
11. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
12. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5
13. the person playing domino is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
14. the bongani-smoker is the townhouse house##1
15. the bongani-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in may##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Cigar         | baccarat     | bongani   | chaman | havana |
| Game   | monopoly | poker   | scrabble   | domino  |
| Birthday         | may  | august  | december  | june |
| House     | ranch-style    | townhouse | palace     | gothic-revival    |

