.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, camping, traveling
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, french, british, chinese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, animation, epic, crime
City: hamburg, edinburgh, new-york, san-francisco
 1. the person watching epic movies is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person watching animation movies##2
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
 6. the chinese is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 7. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
 8. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching musical movies is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
11. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
13. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the french##5
14. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
15. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
16. the british is on the right of the nigerian##1
17. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the right of the person watching animation movies##8
18. the french is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
19. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby      | skydiving | camping | traveling  | drawing  |
| Nationality          | chinese     | french | nigerian | british  |
