 2. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the colonial house##5
 3. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 4. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the person who likes amber##8
 6. the cottage house is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 9. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes green##1
10. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes amber is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
12. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| House         | cape-cod    | cottage   | colonial | gothic-revival |
| Color   | amber     | blood-red  | yellow   | green      |
