 4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 6. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 7. the person who likes green is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 8. the person drinking milk is the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
10. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
11. the person who likes azure is between the person who's birthday is in september and the owner of the hamster##2
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
13. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
14. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

